No. 10-6551. LaVern Berryhill, Petitioner v. James Hardy Payne, Judge, United States District Court for the Northern District of Oklahoma, et al. 562 U.S. 999, 131 S. Ct. 554,

178 L. Ed. 2d 367,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8375. November 1, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
